The paper proposes a novel algorithm for solving the Graph-Constrained Coalition Formation (GCCF) problem, which involves modeling the search space as a rooted tree and efficiently parallelizing the algorithm. This suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.SI" (Social and Information Networks).
